00:19:22.583 --> 00:19:27.255
Then father understands that this one is not going to be handled easily.

00:19:27.280 --> 00:19:29.455
So, he plays the trick on him.

00:19:29.464 --> 00:19:32.346
He says, “All right. Let it be at the back.

00:19:32.355 --> 00:19:37.114
But you think, you believe that

00:19:37.139 --> 00:19:40.007
it is the horse which is pulling the cart.

00:19:40.008 --> 00:19:41.682
You believe it.”

00:19:42.032 --> 00:19:44.797
Now how Krishna has said it is even beautifully,

00:19:44.822 --> 00:19:46.378
more beautifully than this analogy.

00:19:46.403 --> 00:19:49.904
I gave you this analogy to see the trick of Shri Krishna.

00:19:49.928 --> 00:19:52.805
And He had to play because people are so mediocre.

00:19:52.830 --> 00:19:57.587
Since the six thousand years they have been believing into something nonsensical,

00:19:57.616 --> 00:20:00.419
that you will see now.

00:20:00.501 --> 00:20:05.549
He [Arjuna] said that,

00:20:05.713 --> 00:20:08.680
“If I kill people,

00:20:08.713 --> 00:20:11.470
then I will have the karmas within me.

00:20:11.495 --> 00:20:15.864
And after my Realization – how will I get my Realization?

00:20:15.889 --> 00:20:19.748
If I get my Realization, then I cannot kill.”

00:20:19.773 --> 00:20:23.084
These were his ideas about Realization.

00:20:23.109 --> 00:20:26.049
What Krishna said that,

00:20:26.081 --> 00:20:30.067
“You get your Realization, and then

00:20:30.092 --> 00:20:35.797
whatever you do is in the name, is really, fully in order to God.

00:20:36.194 --> 00:20:38.141
If you have to kill, you have to kill!

00:20:38.150 --> 00:20:41.636
You have to kill the devils; you have to kill the rakshasas.”

00:20:41.645 --> 00:20:44.760
The idea that if you kill somebody, it’s something wrong –

00:20:44.785 --> 00:20:46.540
I mean, supposing today,

00:20:46.556 --> 00:20:50.900
Hitler was to come, to spare him physically is wrong.

00:20:50.917 --> 00:20:52.801
Will you spare a snake?

00:20:52.826 --> 00:20:54.034
You will have to kill.

00:20:54.059 --> 00:20:56.756
And He said, “Nobody is killed there” and that’s a fact.

00:20:56.781 --> 00:20:57.861
Nobody dies.

00:20:57.886 --> 00:21:02.499
As I told you that the Spirits cannot be killed

00:21:02.524 --> 00:21:07.568
[unsure] this will only put them out of the stage just now.

00:21:07.935 --> 00:21:14.426
So Krishna says that, “You should first become Realized,

00:21:14.442 --> 00:21:18.509
become a witness, then you are just an instrument in the hands of God.

00:21:18.534 --> 00:21:22.600
And He uses you for what He likes, and you do whatever He says.

00:21:22.611 --> 00:21:25.009
If He says you have to kill, you have to kill.

00:21:25.018 --> 00:21:27.242
If He says don’t kill, you don’t kill.

00:21:27.267 --> 00:21:29.102
Because the power starts flowing through you.

00:21:29.127 --> 00:21:32.420
Now, your own concept of compassion is wrong.

00:21:32.428 --> 00:21:34.622
How can you be compassionate with people,

00:21:34.647 --> 00:21:37.370
that one man can destroy the whole world?

00:21:37.395 --> 00:21:41.024
Are you to be compassionate to that man? For what?

00:21:41.049 --> 00:21:44.607
The greatest compassion is to him, is to put him out.

00:21:44.989 --> 00:21:48.802
After all controls, God is watching.

00:21:48.829 --> 00:21:51.582
This is the way to stop action.

00:21:52.157 --> 00:21:54.706
That is what Krishna said.

00:21:56.338 --> 00:21:58.103
But Arjuna didn’t understand.

00:21:58.151 --> 00:22:03.033
He said, “Still, how can get rid of karmas?’,

00:22:03.058 --> 00:22:05.646
and he had those theories.

00:22:05.988 --> 00:22:08.650
How to get rid of the karma.

00:22:08.921 --> 00:22:10.711
So Krishna played a trick with him.

00:22:10.719 --> 00:22:12.568
He said, “All right” .

00:22:13.673 --> 00:22:16.007
He put a very absurd condition.

00:22:16.032 --> 00:22:20.186
This is what is the essence of diplomacy is to put an absurd condition

00:22:20.200 --> 00:22:22.243
and befool a person

00:22:22.395 --> 00:22:25.771
so that when he reaches a stage and understands

00:22:25.796 --> 00:22:28.139
that it’s absurd, then he gives it up.

00:22:28.155 --> 00:22:30.014
Otherwise, he will not.

00:22:30.602 --> 00:22:34.836
So, He told Arjuna that,

00:22:35.575 --> 00:22:37.902
“Very good,

00:22:38.357 --> 00:22:41.438
you do not want Realization, go ahead.

00:22:41.494 --> 00:22:43.996
You do all your karmas.

00:22:44.124 --> 00:22:48.913
And you put the fruit of the karmas at the lotus feet of the God.

00:22:48.971 --> 00:22:52.250
That’s what you do, so you won’t have any karmas upon yourself.”

00:22:52.275 --> 00:22:54.093
This is an absurd thing.

00:22:54.118 --> 00:22:58.353
Before Realization, it cannot happen. It cannot happen.

00:22:58.370 --> 00:23:02.277
Before Realization, your ego remains as it is, as you see,

00:23:02.302 --> 00:23:04.422
it is not sucked in.

00:23:04.644 --> 00:23:06.250
Subtler it will become,

00:23:06.275 --> 00:23:09.896
you’ll become very humble and very kind and this,

00:23:09.921 --> 00:23:12.495
but still the ego is there.

00:23:12.869 --> 00:23:16.196
Ego is there means, it’s a state of your mind,

00:23:16.200 --> 00:23:18.390
which is covered with ego.

00:23:18.692 --> 00:23:24.458
It has to be sucked in by the actualization and actual happening.

00:23:24.538 --> 00:23:26.592
Not just saying that, “Oh you are very humble”.

00:23:26.617 --> 00:23:29.385
Some of the egoistical people are extremely humble

00:23:29.410 --> 00:23:32.897
because that suits them, extremely.

00:23:32.977 --> 00:23:37.448
But inside it’s the ego there.
Ego is there.

00:23:37.999 --> 00:23:40.018
Till it is sucked in, you cannot fight it,

00:23:40.027 --> 00:23:42.741
you cannot drive it out, you cannot get out of it.

00:23:42.766 --> 00:23:44.878
It has to be sucked in.

00:23:45.220 --> 00:23:47.858
To suck that ego,

00:23:47.994 --> 00:23:50.735
kundalini has to rise,
you have to get your Realization.

00:23:50.743 --> 00:23:55.270
You have to become the Self and not the ego, your identification with ego must drop.

00:23:55.302 --> 00:23:58.614
That’s only possible if you become the Spirit.

00:23:58.639 --> 00:24:02.214
But He said, “All right, doesn’t matter. What you do,

00:24:02.239 --> 00:24:06.670
is to do your karmas.
Then go on hitting the cart

00:24:06.695 --> 00:24:09.429
but put all your attention on the horse,

00:24:09.454 --> 00:24:14.721
and your cart will move”. It will never move is the point, the absurdities.

00:24:14.746 --> 00:24:18.334
So He gave such a proposition by which

00:24:18.346 --> 00:24:22.061
the horse does not move.

00:24:22.086 --> 00:24:25.246
And after some time you find, “What is it?

00:24:25.272 --> 00:24:26.536
The cart is just there.

00:24:26.561 --> 00:24:27.680
I am putting everything

00:24:27.705 --> 00:24:30.942
I am supposed to be putting everything on the horse.

00:24:30.960 --> 00:24:32.509
Nothing doing.

00:24:32.525 --> 00:24:35.075
It’s not connected. It is just there.”

00:24:35.100 --> 00:24:37.259
Once this confusion is reached

00:24:37.276 --> 00:24:40.358
then you take your Realization and actualization.

00:24:40.398 --> 00:24:42.018
This is the point.

00:24:42.201 --> 00:24:47.843
Unless and until this absurdity is dawned upon you,

00:24:47.852 --> 00:24:49.661
you will never accept.

00:24:50.098 --> 00:24:51.854
Because you are asking questions,

00:24:51.872 --> 00:24:54.754
“Why should you do it?” “Why should he do it?” “Why?”

00:24:54.787 --> 00:24:56.923
So He says, “All right, go ahead.”

00:24:56.931 --> 00:24:59.283
So this is the karma theory that started,

00:24:59.299 --> 00:25:04.564
that whatever karmas you do, you put at the lotus feet of God.

00:25:07.000 --> 00:25:08.443
So it’s a misbelief.

00:25:08.468 --> 00:25:11.969
He put you into a maya, into illusion.

00:25:12.481 --> 00:25:14.053
That was important.

00:25:14.077 --> 00:25:17.103
At that stage, it was important to put you into illusion.

00:25:17.128 --> 00:25:19.231
Because you would not accept even.

00:25:19.488 --> 00:25:22.926
See, if you have to take out the butter,

00:25:23.183 --> 00:25:26.120
you cannot do it with a straight finger, you have to make

00:25:26.123 --> 00:25:29.178
your finger bent a little, it’s like that.

00:25:30.452 --> 00:25:34.803
So, Arjuna said, “What about dharma?

00:25:34.892 --> 00:25:36.610
What about devotion to God?

00:25:36.635 --> 00:25:39.539
These are organized visions, churches,

00:25:39.564 --> 00:25:42.661
and our temples and all.
What about that?”

00:25:42.686 --> 00:25:45.450
Till that also, he was [?].

00:25:45.475 --> 00:25:48.722
He says that, “Patram pushpam phalam toyam yo me.”

00:25:48.733 --> 00:25:50.956
“Whatever is the fruit,

00:25:50.981 --> 00:25:55.158
whatever is the flower,

00:25:55.183 --> 00:25:58.440
or whatever is the water you give me, I will take it.

00:25:58.465 --> 00:26:01.928
I’ll take all that. But if you give me a flower, I’ll take it.”

00:26:01.953 --> 00:26:05.043
But by giving, He is very clever,

00:26:05.068 --> 00:26:08.045
which I don’t know if people have seen the point or not.

00:26:08.064 --> 00:26:10.525
He says, “By giving, who says

00:26:10.542 --> 00:26:15.872
at that you do ‘ananya bhakti’, emotion that is ‘ananya’.

00:26:16.321 --> 00:26:19.793
Now the word ‘ananya’ is the word,

00:26:19.818 --> 00:26:23.987
which is the real devotion: a-nanya,

00:26:24.012 --> 00:26:27.720
it means when you are not the other,

00:26:27.930 --> 00:26:30.440
when you are Realized.

00:26:30.465 --> 00:26:34.569
You can only do bhakti when you are Realized, ananya.

00:26:34.602 --> 00:26:37.906
The person who’s ananya, means the one who is not the other:

00:26:37.917 --> 00:26:42.005
you become one with God, then you do the bhakti.

00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:47.265
Very clearly, He said that, “You do ananya bhakti”.

00:26:47.290 --> 00:26:50.961
Ananya devotion, means devotion

00:26:50.985 --> 00:26:52.941
when you are not the other, when you are Realized.

00:26:52.966 --> 00:26:55.559
Before that, what’s the devotion?

00:26:55.584 --> 00:26:59.032
Very cleverly said, but nobody sees the point.

00:26:59.057 --> 00:27:00.780
I’ve been asking people;

00:27:00.789 --> 00:27:03.625
the other day a gentleman came from a cult,

00:27:03.650 --> 00:27:07.921
“What does mean Shri Rama, Shri Krishna, Shri Rama, Shri Krishna.”

00:27:07.946 --> 00:27:10.401
This is not ananya bhakti.

00:27:10.426 --> 00:27:14.683
Ananya bhakti means when there is no other,

00:27:14.700 --> 00:27:17.415
means you become Realized.

00:27:20.231 --> 00:27:25.411
This is the essence of this bhakti Yoga.

00:27:26.785 --> 00:27:28.715
In bhakti Yoga, He has said that,

00:27:28.740 --> 00:27:31.948
“You have to become one with your Spirit.”

00:27:31.973 --> 00:27:35.635
Also by saying ananya, and by karmas,

00:27:35.660 --> 00:27:37.496
Karma Yoga is also the same type,

00:27:37.521 --> 00:27:41.212
“Whatever work you do you put at the lotus feet of the Lord.”

00:27:41.237 --> 00:27:44.167
You cannot do it, absurd condition.

00:27:45.433 --> 00:27:49.434
But after Realization, what happens to you that

00:27:49.459 --> 00:27:51.223
you do not say, “I do it”.

00:27:51.248 --> 00:27:53.114
You say, “It’s moving”, “It’s coming”,

00:27:53.139 --> 00:27:56.274
“It’s rising”, “It’s starting”. “It”, third person.

00:27:57.302 --> 00:27:58.940
You just say “it”.

00:27:58.965 --> 00:28:02.215
“I am getting the kundalini”, you don’t say, never.

00:28:02.240 --> 00:28:05.027
“It is coming”, because you know you are not, you feel that.

00:28:05.052 --> 00:28:08.474
Because its flowing from you, you have become aware of that.

00:28:09.019 --> 00:28:12.415
You say, “It is going”, “It is coming”, “It is not coming”.

00:28:12.426 --> 00:28:15.857
You don’t say, “I am giving Realization to myself or to anybody”.

00:28:15.882 --> 00:28:18.096
Like a lady came with Me to America.

00:28:18.121 --> 00:28:21.703
And she told Me that, “Mother, You must give Realization to my son”.

00:28:21.713 --> 00:28:23.888
I said, “All right.

00:28:24.470 --> 00:28:26.598
Let him come.” He came all the way from [inaudible],

00:28:26.623 --> 00:28:29.758
and the kundalini was frozen, it wouldn’t rise.

00:28:29.783 --> 00:28:31.746
She said, “Mother please give him Realization.”

00:28:31.771 --> 00:28:34.741
I said, “You are a Realized soul. You try to treat him”.

00:28:34.766 --> 00:28:37.021
Or give him a certificate that he is a Realized soul.

00:28:37.046 --> 00:28:39.372
She said, “How can I do? He is not.

00:28:39.995 --> 00:28:41.377
And why not?

00:28:41.400 --> 00:28:44.899
It’s a good idea, you are listening to my recording morning till evening, to give him Realization.

00:28:44.924 --> 00:28:47.688
You say you are Realised. Why do you say you are Realized?

00:28:47.713 --> 00:28:50.472
If I were you, I would say, “Baba you are Realized. Now get out of here”.

00:28:50.497 --> 00:28:56.295
Because I knew that  the Kundalini doesn’t rise. It’s a frozen kundalini.

00:28:56.994 --> 00:28:58.676
I said, “Why don’t you do it?”

00:28:58.701 --> 00:29:00.909
She said, “How can I?” I know she is not Realized.

00:29:00.926 --> 00:29:05.413
She doesn’t give vibrations. How can I take?” I said, “That’s what it is.”

00:29:05.438 --> 00:29:08.448
The kundalini has to rise.

00:29:08.895 --> 00:29:13.286
That means that you know it is beyond your ego.

00:29:13.401 --> 00:29:15.916
It is beyond you.

00:29:15.950 --> 00:29:18.053
You cannot do it.

00:29:19.869 --> 00:29:24.650
You must have that authority within you, then only you can do it.

00:29:24.857 --> 00:29:27.383
As long as there is authority.

00:29:27.415 --> 00:29:29.093
You are doing it, that’s why that

00:29:29.110 --> 00:29:33.619
ego means an illusion that you are doing something.

00:29:33.644 --> 00:29:35.553
Because you don’t do anything.

00:29:35.577 --> 00:29:36.555
What do you do?

00:29:36.580 --> 00:29:38.396
As I told you, all dead work.

00:29:38.412 --> 00:29:39.753
Dead to the dead.

00:29:39.778 --> 00:29:43.591
You make a chair or a staircase, “Oh you are a great man!”.

00:29:43.616 --> 00:29:46.293
So [inaudible] from the mountains, make another mountain,

00:29:46.317 --> 00:29:48.950
“Oh you are a great architect”.

00:29:48.975 --> 00:29:50.747
All these are dead energies

00:29:50.772 --> 00:29:54.716
you are handling, electricity, magnetism, architecture studies.

00:29:54.732 --> 00:29:57.544
All these things are not living energies.

00:29:58.483 --> 00:30:02.406
Living energy is the synthesis energy of all the energies.

00:30:03.121 --> 00:30:06.840
It is ‘prana’ on the right-hand side.

00:30:06.865 --> 00:30:10.122
On the left-hand side is the ‘mana’,

00:30:10.147 --> 00:30:13.855
and in the center is the dharma.

00:30:13.874 --> 00:30:18.266
All these three energies are synthesized

00:30:18.291 --> 00:30:21.618
are integrated, I should say [Inaudible]

00:30:21.633 --> 00:30:23.415
...is again dead to the dead.

00:30:23.424 --> 00:30:26.530
But we can get completely integrated

00:30:26.555 --> 00:30:30.931
when the light of the Spirit comes in you,

00:30:30.933 --> 00:30:32.346
and this is the Brahma,

00:30:32.371 --> 00:30:34.519
is the one that is flowing through your hands,

00:30:34.544 --> 00:30:37.656
is the Brahma Shakti, is the Brahma.

00:30:39.885 --> 00:30:41.615
So this was about Gita.

00:30:41.640 --> 00:30:43.926
But in his childhood, what did He do?

00:30:43.951 --> 00:30:45.658
We have to understand.

00:30:45.683 --> 00:30:49.717
In his childhood, people say He just tried some things.

00:30:49.742 --> 00:30:51.765
No He was not.

