And He would just break that

00:32:37.776 --> 00:32:39.309
pitcher from the back,

00:32:39.318 --> 00:32:42.057
so the water would fall on the back

00:32:42.060 --> 00:32:45.355
giving them Realisation;

00:32:45.380 --> 00:32:47.936
see the trick of the child.

