01:22:13.696 --> 01:22:17.828
If you show the cross the devils run away. It’s common.

01:22:18.427 --> 01:22:22.646
He controls our ego on the right-hand side.

01:22:22.666 --> 01:22:25.716
Though the Christians are the most ego oriented.

01:22:25.732 --> 01:22:31.792
Whatever they profess, they are just the opposite.

01:22:33.097 --> 01:22:38.284
And then He controls the dharma within us by which

01:22:38.300 --> 01:22:44.469
He makes us rise above towards spirituality, to be our Spirit.

01:22:44.494 --> 01:22:47.310
He controls that center within us.

01:22:47.327 --> 01:22:52.727
And this center is the center where your eyes get pure,

01:22:53.008 --> 01:22:57.671
that your superego at the back is clear,

01:22:58.806 --> 01:23:02.008
that your ego is sucked in,

01:23:02.025 --> 01:23:07.757
and from your eyes flows nothing but just compassion.

01:23:07.782 --> 01:23:11.859
Just compassion, and love of God

01:23:11.867 --> 01:23:16.569
and the devotees have adoration and nothing else.

01:23:17.978 --> 01:23:22.903
One lecture is not sufficient to describe Christ.

01:23:22.928 --> 01:23:28.870
Nor it is sufficient to describe Shri Krishna.

01:23:29.188 --> 01:23:33.897
I have spoken for hours, days together,

01:23:34.360 --> 01:23:36.791
and this lecture has taken too much time

01:23:36.799 --> 01:23:44.104
because I have tackled two very important centers together.

01:23:44.113 --> 01:23:48.235
I hope you will not sit on certain words

01:23:48.260 --> 01:23:54.306
or certain thoughts and just try to renounce the truth.

01:23:54.314 --> 01:23:56.362
This is the truth.

01:23:56.387 --> 01:23:59.112
I have come here to tell you the truth

01:23:59.124 --> 01:24:05.652
and not to please you, your ego, to please your ego,

01:24:05.804 --> 01:24:12.459
or to excite your superego, but to comfort you.

01:24:12.682 --> 01:24:17.058
And to make you your Self, your Spirit.

01:24:17.083 --> 01:24:19.410
May God bless you all.

